        <updateDate>2021-08-11T15:35:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Federal Firearm Licensing Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a federal firearm licensing program through which an individual must obtain a federal firearm license from the Department of Justice prior to purchasing or receiving a firearm. To be eligible for such a license, the individual must have completed training in firearms safety and be subject to a background investigation and criminal history check.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
